text: Valeria Caracuta (born 14 December 1987 in San Pietro Vernotico) is an Italian volleyball player. She played at the 2013 Mediterranean Games, 2013 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2015 European Games. She played for River Volley, SAB Volley, Golem Volley, and Volley Busto Arsizio. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Italian volleyball players
